  "hint": "The LSB (Q₀) always toggles: D₀ = NOT(Q₀). The MSB depends on direction: counting UP toggles Q₁ when Q₀=1, counting DOWN toggles Q₁ when Q₀=0. Smart formula: D₁ = Q₁ XOR Q₀ XOR Dir.",
